### Test 14: Edit Profile - With Valid Token
# First login to get a token, then replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with the actual token
POST http://localhost:5500/api/auth/edit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "newEmail": "newemail@example.com"
}

